**[Blockonomics.co](https://www.blockonomics.co)** is an easy to use bitcoin financial tracker. It enables users to watch balances/transactions of multiple addresses without requiring private key.

## Features

### Address Watcher

**[Blockonomics.co](https://www.blockonomics.co)** provides an easy to use address watcher. User can add public bitcoin [[addresses|Address]] and also label them using tags. Dashboard shows a quick overview of balances classified by each tag. Balance is shown in BTC as well as currency of users' choice

### Transaction History
Graph of balance is shown for various time periods. History of [[transactions|Transactions]] involved is shown along with the graph. Pending transactions tab shows [[transactions|Transactions]] happening on user [[addresses|Address]] that are unconfirmed or partially confirmed (one confirmation)

### Notifications

User can subscribe to email notifications, showing summary of [[transactions|Transactions]] that happened in the last block. Email is sent only after 2 confirmations. 


